metadata.name: Rainbow Tangle
metadata.description:
our love is lighter than the feathers of a dove in the sunrise.
our love is darker than the wing of a raven in the night.
through our touch a burst of chromaphilia is born 
bursting like a bomb within us
igniting an eternal rainbow flowing through our veins like blood, like honey, like nectar
encapsulating us in bliss
the moon is our voyuer tonight
